<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-orange);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Fabric &amp; Building Envelope</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Façade &amp; Cladding</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">The full façade scope, self-delivered — rainscreen cladding, curtain walling, render, brickwork and EWI. With the Building Safety Act reshaping how external walls are specified and built, our compliance-led approach to fire performance and traceability is the reason to put façade work with us.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Façade &amp; Cladding →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Façade &amp; Cladding,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>Rainscreen cladding systems</li><li>Curtain walling</li><li>Render &amp; through-coloured systems</li><li>Brickwork &amp; repointing</li><li>External wall insulation (EWI)</li><li>Glazing &amp; window replacement</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>Building Regulations Part L (thermal) &amp; Part B (fire)</li><li>BS 8414 &amp; BR 135 — cladding fire performance</li><li>CWCT standards — curtain walling &amp; cladding</li><li>PAS 2030 / 2035 — retrofit &amp; EWI</li><li>CDM 2015 throughout</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>How do you ensure cladding fire compliance?</summary><p>We specify and install systems with cladding fire performance assessed to BS 8414 against the BR 135 criteria, designed to meet Building Regulations Part B. Product data and records are retained for the building's safety case.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you carry out external wall insulation and retrofit?</summary><p>Yes. We deliver EWI and fabric retrofit within the PAS 2030 / 2035 framework, improving thermal performance to Part L while keeping the fire strategy and detailing correct.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you work on occupied buildings and at height safely?</summary><p>Yes. We plan access with scaffold, MEWPs and mast-climbers and sequence the works elevation-by-elevation under CDM 2015, keeping residents and the public safe around live buildings.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of Fabric &amp; Building Envelope</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="sector" href="/fabric/">Fabric &amp; Building Envelope overview</a><a class="sector" href="/fabric/roofing/">Roofing</a><a class="sector" 